extendedInfo.description: Hey!Many colorful Soap bubbles are flying towards you from far.Try to touch them, you might get a little surprise!This is our first 3D wallpaper developed by our own 3D engine, with no ads.We would appreciate your encouragement and suggestions, so send us an email at your convenience.Additional notes:The dream bubbles live wallpaper is used as with other live wallpapers, you can easily switch wallpaper on your phone's wallpaper setup page .*Download and install, and then select Menu -> Wallpaper -> Live wallpaper -> Dream BubblesWe launched a Professional Edition for this wallpaper where you can set and alter the background picture from various senses we provide! If you really like the live wallpaper, please support us by buying Professional Edition: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.easy3d.wallpaper, thank you very much! With your support we will develop more and better live wallpaper!We will update the background image every Friday by releasing a small version, if you have a favorite picture as the background, you can send mail directly (change.3dwallpaper@gmail.com) to us.Image Requirements: HD pictures in black and white figuresPlease give us more suggestions, we do it better together! Our email is change.3dwallpaper@gmail.com, Thank you!Keyword:bubble beautiful bubble soap bubble HD beauty beautiful 3D live wallpaper realistic soap bubble Solo Launcher go launcher go wallpaper
